item.title: What do i do?
item.dc:creator: @Pure_Slay Pure Slay
item.description:
@Pure_Slay wrote:

Your code’s wrong in your Compiler or Build

Right click it “edit”

You’ll see

[code]@echo off
title **** Compiler
“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0\bin\javac.exe” -cp . *.java

pause[/code]

or something similar… now
open:
My Computer -> C:\ -> program files -> java -> bin

Now copy that url
C:\program files\java\jdk1.6.0\bin
or something similar…
now replace that with the other code, then save.
That will fix it.
